  "text": "The acquisition of the required experimental test data for a large off-road tyre poses numerous challenges. The data is however significant in creating tyre models that are accurately representing the real tyre behaviour. A method of acquiring parameterisation test data, as well as an extensive data set, is discussed in great detail in [CITATION_1] .",
